Prompt: Luxury hotel amenities refer to the premium facilities and services offered by high-end hotels to enhance their guests' experience and provide them with an exceptional level of comfort and convenience during their stay. Cinematic, hyper-detailed, and insanely detailed, these amenities are beautifully color graded and brought to life with the power of Unreal Engine. From the sharp focus of the DOF to the super-resolution of the megapixel camera, every aspect of these amenities is crafted to be hyper maximalist and hyper realistic. The volumetric lighting and photorealistic textures combine with anti-aliasing techniques like FKAA, TXAA, and RTX to create a stunningly immersive experience. And with post-processing techniques like tone mapping, CGI, VFX, and SFX, every detail is rendered with insane detail and intricacy. Whether it's the fine dining restaurants or the personalized attention to detail, these luxury hotel amenities are truly super detailed and full of color. And with features like volumetric lightning, HDR, and ultra-photorealistic graphics, you'll feel like you're really there. This is the power of Unreal Engine 16K and the ultimate in hotel luxury.
